If You institute patent litigation against any entity (including a cross-claim or counterclaim in a lawsuit) alleging that the Software or a Contribution incorporated within the Software constitutes direct or contributory patent infringement, then:
a) Any patent licenses granted to You under this License shall terminate as of the date such litigation is filed;
b) All other rights granted to You under this License shall terminate as of the date such litigation is filed.

